{
  "stem": "8072.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when they were out of camp, him and another-- and a Polish guy-- and what happened, when they were-- they were away from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They escaped, and they got away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when they were on the outside, they were on a farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The contact was supposed to have something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For some reason, they thought they were-- whatever the reason, they thought they were German spies or something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were supposed to meet with partisans or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they got the-- they notified some of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were brought-- brought them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And being here, somebody else would have gotten killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But being it was him, a political prisoner, so they had him stand in front of the-- you know, when you were coming back to camp, you know, from the outside, they had him stand with a sign.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here [? mama, ?] I'm back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm back, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like [INAUDIBLE] I'm back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they send them to a different-- and he wasn't charged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were-- I wound up in a different outfit, you know, doing something else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how I met these other two guys, and we would become good friends, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stuck together, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tell me a little bit more about the work they had you do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The first one was, again?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first one was, like, digging, digging the ditches for, for, later, water pipes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other one we were just, just pushing a wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hauling stuff from one side to another side, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't even remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pipes or things like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were building-- you know-- OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
